Mayor of NY urges citizens to take photos of other citizens who are gathered in groups and not practicing social distancing and send those photos to 311-692 or download the 311 APP , then law enforcement will come and “help” the situation.  For the love of god stop what your doing and read the book published in 1949! By George Orwell titled 1984 , the dystopian world he is speaking of we are living in now. 
To the people of NY please know this is no disrespect when I say this but you must not trade your freedom under the guise of safety, this is exactly what happened with 911 and the patriot act that followed,  exchanging privacy for false security and once those doors open, just like the patriot act, it doesn't close back. .
